ou , Diana , no matter where I am.','你永遠不用許願我愛你，因為我會在這裡，就是因為我愛你。','matter',NULL,47,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(104,'It’s not about deserve , it’s about what you believe. And I believe in love.','這不是值不值得的問題，而是攸關於你相信什麼。而我，相信愛','deserve',NULL,47,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(105,'Tell her that you love her. You’ve got nothing to lose and you’ll always regret it if you don’t.','告訴她你愛她。你沒有什麼好失去的，如果錯過了，你會後悔一輩子。','regret',NULL,48,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(106,'You are perfect and my wasted heart will love you.','對我來說，妳是完美的存在，我一直暗戀著妳。','wasted',NULL,48,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(107,'If you were a melody ,….I used only the good notes.','你若是一首曲子，我願做你動人的音符。','melody',NULL,49,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(108,'That might sound boring , but I think the boring stuff is the stuff I remember the most.','聽起來很無聊，但有時最無聊的小事才是我永遠記得的事。','stuff',NULL,16,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(109,'The supreme happiness of life is the conviction that we are loved; loved for ourselves—say rather , loved in spite of ourselves.','人生最大的幸福，是發現你愛的人正好也愛你； 而且你們沒有錯過。','supreme',NULL,50,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(110,'Thank you , I love you. I knew it in the minute I met you. I’m sorry it took so long for me to catch up. I just got stuck.','我自遇見你那一刻就知道，我愛你。對不起我浪費了太多時間才找到你。','minute',NULL,51,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(111,'There’s only one person that makes me feel like I can fly. That’s you.','只有一個人能讓我覺得我可以飛，那就是你。','makes',NULL,52,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(112,'But the heart’s not like a box that gets filled up . It expands in size the more you love.','人的心不像紙箱一樣，會逐漸被填滿，如果你的愛更多，心的容量也會因此增大，好承接滿溢的愛。','filled up',NULL,53,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(113,'Sometimes it takes more than love to sustain a marriage.','有時候為了維持一段婚姻，付出的要比愛更多。','sustain',NULL,54,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(114,'Life is not the amount of breaths you take , it’s the moments that take your breath away.','人生並不是你呼吸的次數，而是那些令你屏息的時刻。','breaths',NULL,52,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(115,'To me , you are perfect.','對我而言，妳很完美。','perfect',NULL,55,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(116