37'),(526,'Deliberate cruelty is unforgivable, and the onething of which I have never, ever been guilty of.','刻意傷害別人不可原諒，我從未這樣做，也無需因此而感到愧疚。','Deliberate',NULL,217,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(527,'Its what you do right now that makes a difference .','你現在所做的是改變現狀的關鍵。','difference',NULL,218,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(528,'Yes, the past can hurt. But I think you can either run from it or learn from it.','對，過去是痛楚的，但我認為你要麼可以逃避，要麼可以向它學習。 ','either',NULL,10,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(529,'Remember Red, hope is a good thing, maybe the bestof things, and no good thing ever dies.','記住，希望是美好的，可以說是人間至善，而美好的事物是永遠不會消逝的。','hope',NULL,214,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(530,'Reality doesnt change according to your will.','現實不會因為你的意志而改變','according',NULL,219,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(531,'At the edge of the world, his journey begings.','在世界的盡頭，他開始了旅程。','journey',NULL,220,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(532,'You have dreams,you go to protect it.','如果你有夢想，就去守護它。','protect',NULL,206,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(533,'Instead of running from the pain, like a sane person would do, you step into it.','你要迎著疼痛而上，而不是像有理智的人那樣躲避。','Instead',NULL,221,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(534,'You need to believe that something extraordinary is possible.','你要相信，生命中真的存在那些非比尋常的東西。','extraordinary',NULL,222,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(535,'You must always have faith in people, and most importantly you must always have faith in yourself.','你必須對人們有信心，更重要的是必須相信自己。','faith',NULL,223,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(536,'I realise that its actually what happens along the way that counts the stumbles and the falls.','回首成長之路，我明白了：實現夢想的路上充滿挫折','stumbles',NULL,224,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(537,'Our job is improving the quality of life, not just delaying death.','我們要作的是提升生活品質、而不是延緩死亡','quality',NULL,225,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(538,'Sometimes its better to keep certain memories just in your hands.','有些事情還是留在記憶深處比較好。','certain',NULL,226,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(539,'You gotta take chances for the things you care about.','值得為了你在乎的事物冒險','take',NULL,2