-03-18 11:30:37'),(551,'Its Hebrew, its from the Talmud. It says -Whoever saves one life, saves the world entire.','拯救一個人，等於拯救全世界。','entire',NULL,238,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(552,'Fear is the path to the dark side. Fear leads toanger. Anger leads to hate. Hate leads to suffering .','恐懼是墮入原力黑暗面的道路。因為恐懼引發憤怒，憤怒引發仇恨，繼而導致痛苦。','suffering',NULL,239,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(553,'Don\'t hide, don\'t be afraid of the dark，follow the light，then you can make it tomorrow! ','不要躲起來害怕面對，也不要擔憂黑暗，向著光明面走，明日你將克服它。','afraid',NULL,240,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(554,'In every job that must be done, there is an element of fun. You find the fun, and snap, the job is a game.','在每一個必須完成的工作中，都存在著有趣的元素。找到了樂趣和節奏，那這份工作就是個遊戲。','element',NULL,235,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(555,'Lifes a little bit messy . We all make mistakes. No matter what type of animal you are, change starts with you.','生活總會有那麼點不順心，我們都會犯錯。天性如何並不重要，改變都由你開始。','messy',NULL,241,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(556,'Its not who you are underneath, its what you do that defines you.','你真正是誰並不重要，重要的是你的所做所為。','defines',NULL,215,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(557,'Men don\'t follow titles, they follow courage .','人們追隨勇敢者，而不是位高者。','courage',NULL,242,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(558,'If work has no intention , its not work at all. Its an empty motion.','如果工作沒有目標，那就不是工作，而是沒有意義的行動。','intention',NULL,243,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(559,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(560,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(561,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2022-03-18 11:30:37'),(562,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
